        <sponsor name-id="M000312">Mr. McGovern</sponsor> (for himself, <cosponsor name-id="J000255">Mr. Jones</cosponsor>, and <cosponsor name-id="B001245">Ms. Bordallo</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was referred to the <committee-name committee-id="HAS00">Committee on Armed Services</committee-name>
